    longDesc:'El Minibar elevates the tapas format into something close to fine dining. The Iberian ham platter is sourced with care, the goat cheese toast arrives with honey and walnuts, and the cod croquettes are silken inside with a shattering crust. The brioche mini-burgers have developed a cult following among regulars.',
