    address:'Cuesta de Sto. Domingo 8, Centro, 28013 Madrid',mapCoords:'40.4194113,-3.7096198',
    longDesc:'El Rey de los Tacos takes its crown seriously — the al pastor is carved from a slowly rotating trompo, the birria tacos arrive in a rich dark consommé for dipping, and the quesadillas are filled with Oaxacan cheese that pulls into dramatic strings. Horchata is the traditional accompaniment and here it is made fresh daily.',
