    desc:'The definitive Saigon banh mi — longer and crunchier than the Hoi An version, with a lineup of fillings that stretches 20 items deep and queues that prove it.',
    tags:'Banh Mi,Street Food,Saigon',price:'₫30,000',rating:'4.7 ★',
    address:'362 Nguyen Trai, District 1, HCMC',mapCoords:'10.7623,106.6860',
