    desc:'A charming and sacred seaside shrine perched on a natural rocky outcrop at the mouth of Duong Dong River, where local fishermen pray for safe passage and good fortune. Surrounded by colourful fishing boats and a scenic coastal promenade. The nearby night market makes for a perfect sunset-to-evening outing.',
